ChatGPT Agent is a new AI assistant by OpenAI that goes beyond chat. It can take actions, complete tasks, and run apps using a virtual computer built inside ChatGPT. It helps users do things like book meetings, write reports, shop online, and create documents. This article explains what ChatGPT Agent is, how it works, and why it matters for AI, business, and everyday users. https://www.blockchain-council.org/certifications/certified-artificial-intelligence-ai-expert/
